1
00:00:08,900 --> 00:00:10,933
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?

2
00:00:10,966 --> 00:00:13,700
I DON'T KNOW,
BUT IT'S COMING.

3
00:00:13,733 --> 00:00:16,066
[ GRUNTS ]
SHOW YOURSELF!

4
00:00:17,833 --> 00:00:19,633
[ GASPS ]

5
00:00:21,766 --> 00:00:23,200
DAMN YOU!

6
00:00:24,900 --> 00:00:27,033
- FOUL DEMON.
- [ GASPS ]

7
00:00:27,066 --> 00:00:30,000
LEAVE THIS WORLD.
YOU DON'T BELONG HERE!

8
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,300
[ GRUNTS ]

9
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:37,100
IZUMO!
WHAT?
DON'T JUST STAND THERE.

10
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:42,766
- UKE! MIKE!
- [ ROARING ]

11
00:00:43,833 --> 00:00:46,533
[ GRUNTING ]

12
00:01:16,866 --> 00:01:19,100
♪ [ MEN SINGING IN JAPANESE ]

13
00:02:32,907 --> 00:02:34,207
[ SHIEMI ]
GOOD MORNING.

14
00:02:34,241 --> 00:02:36,374
HEY.
GOOD MORNING.

15
00:02:36,407 --> 00:02:38,107
[ SWEEPING ]

16
00:02:38,141 --> 00:02:39,841
HUH?

17
00:02:39,874 --> 00:02:43,007
[ SHIMA ]
OKAY, WHATCHA DOING?

18
00:02:43,041 --> 00:02:45,707
WHAT'S IT LOOK LIKE?
WE'RE CLEANING UP.

19
00:02:45,741 --> 00:02:48,407
SHOULDN'T YOU GUYS
BE HEADING OVER TO CLASS NOW?

20
00:02:48,441 --> 00:02:50,341
WHAT, YOU DIDN'T GET
THE E-MAIL?

21
00:02:50,374 --> 00:02:51,974
HUH?

22
00:02:52,007 --> 00:02:53,307
[ BEEPING ]

23
00:02:53,341 --> 00:02:56,907
I SENT THAT
TO ALL THE EXORCISTS
IN OUR REGION.

24
00:02:56,941 --> 00:02:59,007
I'M AFRAID IT'S AN EMERGENCY.

25
00:03:00,641 --> 00:03:03,474
WHY'D YOU SEND IT TO US?
WE'RE JUST EXWIRES.

26
00:03:03,507 --> 00:03:08,607
THE SITUATION IS SO DIRE,
MY BOY, THAT I FELT WE NEEDED
YOUR ASSISTANCE AS WELL.

27
00:03:08,641 --> 00:03:12,541
A TYPE OF DEMON CALLED GUFU
HAS MANAGED TO INFILTRATE
THE ACADEMY.

28
00:03:12,574 --> 00:03:17,607
SIR PHELES'S PROTECTIVE BARRIER
IS SUPPOSED TO REPEL ANY DEMON
THAT'S MID-LEVEL OR HIGHER,

29
00:03:17,641 --> 00:03:20,341
SO WE HAVE TO FIGURE OUT
HOW IT GOT IN HERE.

30
00:03:20,374 --> 00:03:23,841
A DEMON CAN ONLY CIRCUMVENT
THE BARRIER ONE OF TWO WAYS.

31
00:03:23,874 --> 00:03:26,541
EITHER THE BARRIER
HAS A TEAR IN IT
SOMEWHERE...

32
00:03:26,574 --> 00:03:30,274
OR THERE IS A PERSON
INSIDE THE ACADEMY
WHO LET THE DEMON IN.

33
00:03:30,307 --> 00:03:33,374
SAY WHAT?
WHO'D DO SOMETHING
LIKE THAT AND WHY?

34
00:03:33,407 --> 00:03:36,041
WHO KNOWS?
I HAVE NO IDEA.

35
00:03:36,074 --> 00:03:40,341
NOW, THEN, I'VE ASKED
THE INSTRUCTORS TO INVESTIGATE
THE GUFU'S WHEREABOUTS.

36
00:03:40,374 --> 00:03:44,774
HOWEVER, I'D LIKE YOU EXWIRES
TO PERSONALLY CONDUCT
AN INSPECTION OF THE BARRIER.

37
00:03:44,807 --> 00:03:46,641
[ ALL ]
YES, SIR.

38
00:03:49,241 --> 00:03:51,007
[ GRUNTS ]

39
00:03:51,041 --> 00:03:53,941
NOT YOU, RIN.
YOU'RE STAYING HERE
AND TRAINING SOME MORE.

40
00:03:53,974 --> 00:03:55,007
WHA--

41
00:04:00,474 --> 00:04:02,374
THAT SEAL LOOKS GOOD.

42
00:04:02,407 --> 00:04:04,174
YEAH.
THAT'S ANOTHER ONE.

43
00:04:04,207 --> 00:04:07,007
HEY, HOW MANY
OF THESE BARRIERS
ARE THERE TOTAL?

44
00:04:07,041 --> 00:04:08,207
[ GRUNTS ]

45
00:04:08,241 --> 00:04:11,474
12,000.
[ GROANS ]

46
00:04:11,507 --> 00:04:13,574
OH, MAN. THAT NUMBER
MAKES MY HEAD SPIN.

47
00:04:13,607 --> 00:04:15,374
[ GROANS ]

48
00:04:15,407 --> 00:04:18,841
WE'RE GONNA NEED
ALL THE HELP WE CAN
JUST TO GET THROUGH THIS THING.

49
00:04:18,874 --> 00:04:21,307
WHERE THE HECK'S KONEKO AT?
HE SHOULD BE HELPING.

50
00:04:21,341 --> 00:04:25,707
ALL I KNOW IS THAT BY THE TIME
I WOKE UP THIS MORNING,
HE'D ALREADY LEFT THE DORM.

51
00:04:25,741 --> 00:04:28,874
I'VE BEEN CALLING HIS CELL,
BUT HE'S NOT PICKING IT UP.

52
00:04:28,907 --> 00:04:32,541
HE DIDN'T WANNA COME WITH US
WHEN WE WENT TO FIX KURKIKARA.

53
00:04:32,574 --> 00:04:36,407
I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE HE'S THINKING ABOUT
QUITTING THE CRAM SCHOOL.

54
00:04:36,441 --> 00:04:38,441
OH, YEAH?
LIKE HELL HE IS!

55
00:04:38,474 --> 00:04:40,174
HE MADE A PROMISE, REMEMBER?

56
00:04:40,207 --> 00:04:44,974
SATAN KILLED HIS FAMILY,
AND HE WAS GONNA GET REVENGE
FOR 'EM.

57
00:04:45,007 --> 00:04:47,407
BON.

58
00:04:47,441 --> 00:04:50,307
HE'D NEVER GO BACK
ON HIS WORD.
NO WAY.

59
00:04:56,274 --> 00:04:57,641
[ WINGS FLAPPING ]

60
00:05:02,207 --> 00:05:04,674
[ GROANING ]

61
00:05:06,441 --> 00:05:08,141
[ GUFU ]
DOES IT HURT?

62
00:05:08,174 --> 00:05:10,341
O-OF COURSE IT DOES.

63
00:05:10,374 --> 00:05:12,841
I GOT SHOT.
[ GROANING ]

64
00:05:12,874 --> 00:05:16,341
ALL YOU HAVE TO DO IS ACCEPT ME
AND BULLETS WILL NEVER HURT.

65
00:05:18,207 --> 00:05:20,274
WHY DO YOU REJECT ME?

66
00:05:20,307 --> 00:05:25,807
IF YOU HAD MY POWER,
YOU WOULDN'T HAVE TO FEAR
THE SON OF SATAN ANYMORE.

67
00:05:25,841 --> 00:05:28,607
COME. FIGHT WITH ME.

68
00:05:28,641 --> 00:05:31,574
WE SHALL KILL
THE SON OF SATAN TOGETHER.

69
00:05:31,607 --> 00:05:34,674
NO WAY.
THAT'S NOT WHAT I WANT.

70
00:05:34,707 --> 00:05:37,274
I NEVER WANTED THAT.
I COULD NEVER KILL OKUMURA.

71
00:05:37,307 --> 00:05:42,241
WHY DOES RIN OKUMURA HAVE TO BE
IN THE SAME CLASS AS ME?

72
00:05:42,274 --> 00:05:43,674
[ GASPS ]

73
00:05:45,041 --> 00:05:49,307
WILL HE TAKE AWAY MY FRIENDS
LIKE HIS FATHER TOOK MY FAMILY?

74
00:05:49,341 --> 00:05:54,941
OKUMURA.
HOW DARE HE, HOW DARE HE,
HOW DARE HE, HOW DARE HE!

75
00:05:54,974 --> 00:05:56,407
YOU'RE WRONG!
STOP IT!

76
00:05:56,441 --> 00:05:59,741
[ LAUGHING ]

77
00:05:59,774 --> 00:06:03,807
ACCEPT THE DARKNESS
IN YOUR SOUL.

78
00:06:03,841 --> 00:06:08,507
I'LL LEND YOU MY POWER ANYTIME
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU WISH.

79
00:06:08,541 --> 00:06:11,174
[ GUFU LAUGHING ]

80
00:06:13,174 --> 00:06:14,674
WHERE AM I?

81
00:06:16,307 --> 00:06:18,307
I'VE GOTTA GET BACK.

82
00:06:18,341 --> 00:06:20,307
EVERYONE MUST BE WORRIED
ABOUT ME.

83
00:06:23,574 --> 00:06:28,674
NOTHING TASTES BETTER
THAN REVENGE WHEN YOUR SOUL
IS FILLED WITH HATE.

84
00:06:28,707 --> 00:06:31,274
THAT'S MY CHANCE TO HARVEST IT.

85
00:06:33,384 --> 00:06:35,084
[ RIN GRUNTING ]

86
00:06:35,118 --> 00:06:36,818
[ GROANS ]

87
00:06:36,851 --> 00:06:39,712
COME ON, HOW LONG
AM I SUPPOSED
TO KEEP DOING THIS?

88
00:06:39,712 --> 00:06:44,312
YOU'RE GOING TO KEEP DOING IT
UNTIL YOU FIGURE OUT HOW
TO CONTROL YOUR FLAMES BETTER.

89
00:06:44,345 --> 00:06:46,279
[ GROANS, BLOWS ]

90
00:06:46,312 --> 00:06:48,679
ARE YOU COOL WITH THIS?

91
00:06:48,712 --> 00:06:50,979
SITTING AROUND WHEN THERE'S
A DEMON TO HUNT?

92
00:06:51,012 --> 00:06:54,379
NO, YOU'RE RIGHT.
I'D RATHER BE OUT THERE
TRYING TO FIND THE GUFU.

93
00:06:54,412 --> 00:06:58,345
BUT I'VE BEEN ORDERED
TO KEEP AN EYE ON YOU,
SO I DON'T REALLY HAVE A CHOICE.

94
00:06:58,379 --> 00:07:02,979
WELL, THEN, LET'S BAIL
AND GO HUNTING.
COME ON.

95
00:07:03,012 --> 00:07:04,979
WOULD YOU BE SERIOUS
FOR ONCE?

96
00:07:05,012 --> 00:07:07,412
YOU'RE RUNNING
OUT OF TIME HERE, RIN.

97
00:07:07,445 --> 00:07:10,645
IF YOU THINK EVERYTHING'S
GONNA GO YOUR WAY LIKE IT
ALWAYS HAS, THEN YOU NEED--

98
00:07:10,679 --> 00:07:12,679
- [ GROANS ]
- [ GASPS ]

99
00:07:12,712 --> 00:07:15,112
WHAT'S WRONG?

100
00:07:15,145 --> 00:07:16,745
IT'S NOTHING.

101
00:07:16,779 --> 00:07:19,712
JUST KEEP GOING
WITH YOUR TRAINING.

102
00:07:19,745 --> 00:07:21,245
[ SIGHS ]
YES, SIR.

103
00:07:23,579 --> 00:07:25,279
YEAH, RIGHT, SUCKA.

104
00:07:25,312 --> 00:07:30,345
THE BEST WAY TO IMPROVE
MY SKILLS IS BY GETTING OUT
INTO THE FIELD.

105
00:07:30,379 --> 00:07:32,179
[ SHOUTING, GRUNTS ]

106
00:07:32,212 --> 00:07:33,412
[ GROANING ]

107
00:07:33,445 --> 00:07:35,145
IT'S NOT WHAT IT
LOOKS LIKE, YUKIO.

108
00:07:35,179 --> 00:07:37,245
I SWEAR I WASN'T THINKING
OF DITCHING.

109
00:07:38,445 --> 00:07:40,812
OH, MAN.
YOU SCARED ME.

110
00:07:46,312 --> 00:07:48,179
[ GASPS ]

111
00:07:53,112 --> 00:07:56,112
[ JINGLING ]
[ SHIMA ] MAN, MY FEET
ARE ALL SWOLLEN.

112
00:07:56,145 --> 00:07:58,545
- OH, HEY, TEACH.
- HOW'S IT GOING THERE?

113
00:07:58,579 --> 00:08:02,112
YOU SURVIVING THIS HEAT?
I JUST WASHED MY FACE,
AND IT HELPED A LITTLE.

114
00:08:02,145 --> 00:08:04,579
NEED COLD WATER.

115
00:08:04,612 --> 00:08:07,545
WE CHECKED THE BARRIERS
ON THE WEST SIDE,
AND THEY'RE ALL GOOD.

116
00:08:07,579 --> 00:08:09,645
SO ARE THE ONES
AT THE MAIN GATE.

117
00:08:09,679 --> 00:08:12,512
GREAT JOB.
THANK YOU.
[ SCREAMING ]

118
00:08:12,545 --> 00:08:14,245
HUH?
WHAT HAPPENED?

119
00:08:14,279 --> 00:08:16,145
HEY, WAIT.
HOLD UP, YOU GUYS.

120
00:08:16,179 --> 00:08:18,812
[ GASPING ]

121
00:08:18,845 --> 00:08:20,512
KONEKOMARU! WHAT HAPPENED?

122
00:08:20,545 --> 00:08:23,945
AH! I DON'T KNOW.
IT'S OKUMURA.
HE JUST CAME AFTER ME.

123
00:08:23,979 --> 00:08:26,512
HUH?

124
00:08:26,545 --> 00:08:29,312
WATCH OUT, SUGURO.
GET AWAY FROM HIM.
HE'S DANGEROUS.

125
00:08:29,345 --> 00:08:33,212
YOU DUMBASS.
YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
WHO'S DANGEROUS AROUND HERE.

126
00:08:33,245 --> 00:08:34,979
[ GUFU LAUGHING ]

127
00:08:35,012 --> 00:08:37,412
DAMN IT,
DON'T YOU LAUGH AT ME!

128
00:08:37,445 --> 00:08:39,079
[ MIWA WHIMPERING ]

129
00:08:40,445 --> 00:08:42,812
OKUMURA,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

130
00:08:42,845 --> 00:08:45,645
WHAT'S IT LOOK LIKE?
I'M GONNA SLASH ITS ASS.

131
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:47,845
RIN, STAND DOWN
AND GET AWAY FROM HIM.

132
00:08:47,879 --> 00:08:50,245
WHY ARE YOU POINTING
THAT GUN AT ME?

133
00:08:50,279 --> 00:08:53,012
THERE'S YOUR TARGET.

134
00:08:53,045 --> 00:08:54,612
WHAT THE--

135
00:08:54,645 --> 00:08:56,445
WHOA, COULD YOU GUYS
JUST CHILL?

136
00:08:56,479 --> 00:08:59,312
COME ON,
PUT THOSE THINGS AWAY, HUH?

137
00:09:06,245 --> 00:09:07,845
[ GUFU LAUGHING ]

138
00:09:10,179 --> 00:09:12,312
LEAVE HIM ALONE!

139
00:09:12,345 --> 00:09:14,212
- NO, RIN!
- [ GASPING ]

140
00:09:16,712 --> 00:09:19,679
HEY! ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

141
00:09:20,479 --> 00:09:22,879
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

142
00:09:22,912 --> 00:09:26,145
CONTROL YOURSELF.
IF YOU GO ON ANOTHER RAMPAGE,
THEY'RE GO--

143
00:09:26,179 --> 00:09:27,745
[ GRUNTS ]

144
00:09:27,779 --> 00:09:30,345
I ALREADY TOLD YOU
ONCE, OKUMURA.

145
00:09:30,379 --> 00:09:33,912
IF YOU EVER HURT
ANY OF MY FRIENDS,
I SWORE I'D KILL YOU.

146
00:09:33,945 --> 00:09:36,645
DAMN IT, ARE YOU BLIND
OR SOMETHING?

147
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:38,812
I WAS GOING AFTER THE DEMON.
[ SHIMA ]
KONEKO.

148
00:09:38,845 --> 00:09:40,812
COME ON, WAKE UP, KONEKO.

149
00:09:40,845 --> 00:09:42,812
WHAT DO WE DO?
HE'S NOT WAKING UP?

150
00:09:46,612 --> 00:09:48,212
DON'T WORRY.
HE'S FINE.

151
00:09:48,245 --> 00:09:50,845
HE'S UNCONSCIOUS,
THAT'S ALL.
OH.

152
00:09:53,245 --> 00:09:56,145
THOSE DAMN FLAMES OF YOURS
COULD KILL PEOPLE, YOU JERK.

153
00:09:56,179 --> 00:09:57,312
[ GASPS ]

154
00:09:57,345 --> 00:10:00,045
WHY CAN'T YOU GET THAT
THROUGH YOUR HEAD ALREADY?

155
00:10:00,079 --> 00:10:02,279
GET OUT OF HERE.

156
00:10:11,212 --> 00:10:12,745
[ METALLIC CLANGING ]

157
00:10:12,779 --> 00:10:14,679
[ SLITHERING ]

158
00:10:16,212 --> 00:10:17,179
[ HISSING ]

159
00:10:18,212 --> 00:10:19,145
[ RATTLING ]

160
00:10:20,479 --> 00:10:21,945
LOOKS LIKE HE FOUND SOMETHING.

161
00:10:23,312 --> 00:10:24,545
[ SHURA ]
IS THAT IT?

162
00:10:24,579 --> 00:10:26,145
[ TSUBAKI ]
PLEASE BE CAREFUL.

163
00:10:26,179 --> 00:10:28,412
YOU KNOW GUFUS
ARE TROUBLESOME DEMONS.

164
00:10:28,445 --> 00:10:30,279
YEAH, YEAH, I KNOW.

165
00:10:36,112 --> 00:10:37,879
WHAT THE HELL?

166
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:45,812
I ABSOLUTELY DO NOT LIKE
THE LOOK OF THIS.

167
00:10:45,845 --> 00:10:48,812
AND I BET AN ACADEMY KEY
WAS USED TO OPEN IT.

168
00:10:48,845 --> 00:10:51,479
IF THIS DOOR CLOSES,
WE WON'T BE ABLE
TO GET BACK,

169
00:10:51,512 --> 00:10:53,479
AND I'LL NEVER SEE
MY KITTY CAT AGAIN.

170
00:10:53,512 --> 00:10:57,312
WELL, YOU GOT A POINT.
WHY DON'T YOU HANG OUT HERE
AND HOLD IT OPEN?

171
00:10:57,345 --> 00:11:00,079
WAIT!
MISS KIRIGAKURE!

172
00:11:00,112 --> 00:11:03,412
COME BACK!

173
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:15,445
[ SHIVERING ]
DAMN, IT'S SO COLD.

174
00:11:18,612 --> 00:11:20,145
[ GASPS ]
HUH?

175
00:11:28,612 --> 00:11:30,812
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS PLACE?

176
00:11:45,914 --> 00:11:48,314
[ GROANING ]

177
00:11:50,013 --> 00:11:51,680
[ SUGURO ]
HEY, YOU'RE UP.

178
00:11:51,713 --> 00:11:53,513
BON!
[ GROANS ]

179
00:11:53,546 --> 00:11:55,746
EASY. YOU'RE NOT GOING
ANYWHERE.

180
00:11:55,780 --> 00:11:57,246
[ GROANS ]

181
00:12:02,313 --> 00:12:06,846
- WHERE AM I?
- YOU'RE AT TRUE CROSS
GENERAL HOSPITAL.

182
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:10,213
ANYWAY, I DIDN'T SEE YOU
ALL DAY, SO I WAS WONDERING,

183
00:12:10,246 --> 00:12:12,746
WHERE THE HECK
DID YOU DISAPPEAR TO?

184
00:12:15,013 --> 00:12:16,946
[ GROANING ]

185
00:12:16,980 --> 00:12:18,480
I CAN'T REMEMBER ANYTHING.

186
00:12:18,513 --> 00:12:20,813
YEAH, OKAY.

187
00:12:20,846 --> 00:12:22,313
JUST TRY TO GET
SOME REST TONIGHT,

188
00:12:22,346 --> 00:12:24,913
AND BY TOMORROW YOU SHOULD BE
GOOD AS NEW.

189
00:12:24,946 --> 00:12:27,146
BON.
WHAT IS IT?

190
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:29,913
IT'S ABOUT OKUMURA.

191
00:12:29,946 --> 00:12:34,180
I-- WELL, WHAT DO YOU THINK
ABOUT HIM?

192
00:12:34,213 --> 00:12:36,980
WHAT DO I THINK?
ABOUT THAT IDIOT?
HUH?

193
00:12:37,013 --> 00:12:40,113
AFTER ALL THE CRAP HE'S PULLED,
THAT JERK GOES
AND ASKS ME TO TRUST HIM.

194
00:12:40,146 --> 00:12:41,680
CAN YOU BELIEVE THAT?

195
00:12:41,713 --> 00:12:45,313
I MEAN, IF YOU WANT SOMEONE
TO TRUST YOU, Y-Y-YOU KNOW,
YOU--

196
00:12:45,346 --> 00:12:47,613
YOU GOTTA HAVE
SOMETHING MORE THAN THAT.

197
00:12:47,646 --> 00:12:49,913
BUT THAT GUY,
HE'S GOT NOTHING ELSE
TO OFFER.

198
00:12:49,946 --> 00:12:52,646
[ EXHALES ]
I'M SCARED.

199
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:56,880
JUST KNOWING THERE'S SOMEONE
LIKE OKUMURA OUT THERE
TERRIFIES ME.

200
00:12:56,913 --> 00:12:59,680
AH, HE'S NOTHING
BUT A MORON.

201
00:12:59,713 --> 00:13:04,546
I MEAN, SURE, HIS POWER CAN BE
PRETTY SCARY, BUT IN THE END,
THAT GUY?

202
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:07,413
NAH, HE'S ABOUT
AS CLUELESS AS THEY COME.

203
00:13:07,446 --> 00:13:09,546
IT'S SILLY
TO BE SCARED OF HIM.

204
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,913
BUT IS THAT THE PROBLEM?

205
00:13:11,946 --> 00:13:14,180
- MAYBE YOU WANNA QUIT.
- [ GASPS ]

206
00:13:14,213 --> 00:13:17,713
YOU WANT ME TO REMIND YOU
ABOUT WHY YOU CAME HERE
IN THE FIRST PLACE?

207
00:13:17,746 --> 00:13:21,113
YOU HEARD THE STORY
ABOUT HOW YOUR MOM WAS BURNED
ALIVE BY THE BLUE FLAMES.

208
00:13:21,146 --> 00:13:24,513
HOW SHE WAS PREGNANT WITH YOU
AND PROTECTED YOU
TO HER LAST BREATH.

209
00:13:24,546 --> 00:13:28,180
SHE DIED PROTECTING YOU.
SHE LOVED YOU THAT MUCH.
YOU KNOW THAT, RIGHT?

210
00:13:28,213 --> 00:13:30,680
I KNOW.
I JUST CAN'T--

211
00:13:30,713 --> 00:13:33,080
[ SIGHS ]

212
00:13:33,113 --> 00:13:34,613
I'M HEADING OUT.

213
00:13:34,646 --> 00:13:38,213
STILL GOT ABOUT 6,000
BARRIERS TO CHECK.

214
00:13:38,246 --> 00:13:41,546
UH, BON.
YOUR SHIRT--
WHAT HAPPENED TO IT?

215
00:13:41,580 --> 00:13:43,146
HUH? OH, THAT.

216
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,613
WAS IT WHEN--

217
00:13:46,646 --> 00:13:48,313
IT'S NO BIG DEAL.

218
00:13:48,346 --> 00:13:50,713
ALL I GOTTA DO
IS BUY ANOTHER SHIRT.
IT'S COOL.

219
00:13:51,946 --> 00:13:53,713
[ WHIMPERING ]
[ GUFU ]
YOU SEE?

220
00:13:53,746 --> 00:13:57,246
THAT IS WHAT HAPPENS
WHEN YOU DON'T DO AS I ASK.

221
00:13:57,280 --> 00:14:00,580
HE IS STILL DANGEROUS.

222
00:14:00,613 --> 00:14:03,580
THE TRAGEDY OF THE BLUE NIGHT
WILL BE REPEATED.

223
00:14:03,613 --> 00:14:05,246
NO.

224
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:09,546
YOUR FRIENDS ARE PRECIOUS.
YOU DON'T WANT TO LOSE THEM,
DO YOU?

225
00:14:09,580 --> 00:14:12,513
ACCEPT ME. NOW.

226
00:14:12,546 --> 00:14:16,513
THEN YOU MUST KILL HIM.
YOU MUST KILL THE SON OF SATAN.

227
00:14:16,546 --> 00:14:18,180
[ WHIMPERING ]

228
00:14:18,213 --> 00:14:20,646
- [ SCREAMING ]
- [ GRUNTS ]
WHAT THE--

229
00:14:22,446 --> 00:14:23,480
[ GASPS ]

230
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:30,113
KONEKOMARU!

231
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:36,380
HEY, BON. I JUST GOT BACK
FROM THE CONVENIENCE STORE
DOWN THE HILL.

232
00:14:36,413 --> 00:14:38,413
I FIGURED KONEKO
WAS GETTING BORED,

233
00:14:38,446 --> 00:14:40,913
SO I GOT SOME STUFF
TO STIMULATE
THAT BIG BRAIN OF HIS.

234
00:14:40,946 --> 00:14:43,013
THERE'S NO TIME
FOR THAT!
HUH?

235
00:14:43,046 --> 00:14:45,713
KONEKOMARU'S BEING POSSESSED
BY A DEMON.

236
00:14:45,746 --> 00:14:47,213
HUH?
I'M GOING AFTER HIM.

237
00:14:47,246 --> 00:14:49,480
GO GET MR. OKUMURA.
HURRY.

238
00:14:49,513 --> 00:14:51,546
HEY! WAIT UP, BON!

239
00:14:51,580 --> 00:14:53,780
[ THUNDER RUMBLING ]

240
00:14:55,546 --> 00:14:58,713
[ SUGURO ]
THOSE DAMN FLAMES OF YOURS
COULD KILL PEOPLE, YOU JERK.

241
00:14:58,746 --> 00:15:01,513
WHY CAN'T YOU GET THAT
THROUGH YOUR HEAD ALREADY?

242
00:15:01,546 --> 00:15:03,980
[ RIN, THINKING ]
WHAT'S WRONG WITH ME?

243
00:15:04,013 --> 00:15:06,813
WHY AM I ALWAYS DOING THIS?

244
00:15:06,846 --> 00:15:08,646
<i>[ WIND BLOWING ]</i>
[ GASPS ]

245
00:15:13,813 --> 00:15:15,346
IT'S YOU.

246
00:15:15,380 --> 00:15:17,680
[ GROWLS ]

247
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:23,013
GREAT.
WHERE IS HE NOW?

248
00:15:23,046 --> 00:15:25,713
[ CELL PHONE RINGING ]

249
00:15:25,746 --> 00:15:27,813
YES.
OKUMURA SPEAKING.

250
00:15:29,246 --> 00:15:31,646
WAIT. MIWA'S WHAT?

251
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:32,780
RIN!

252
00:15:35,280 --> 00:15:36,746
DIE, DEVIL SPAWN!

253
00:15:36,780 --> 00:15:38,113
[ GROANS ]

254
00:15:38,146 --> 00:15:40,513
- KONEKOMARU!
- MIWA! HOLD IT!

255
00:15:40,546 --> 00:15:42,013
SHUT UP!

256
00:15:42,046 --> 00:15:44,680
WHAT THE HELL IS THIS?
IT'S A WIND BARRIER.

257
00:15:44,713 --> 00:15:48,146
YES. BEHOLD MY NEW POWER.

258
00:15:48,180 --> 00:15:50,613
I'VE BEEN REBORN
FOR ONE PURPOSE--

259
00:15:50,646 --> 00:15:52,913
TO RID THE WORLD
OF THE SON OF SATAN!

260
00:15:52,946 --> 00:15:54,680
[ GRUNTS ]

261
00:15:57,546 --> 00:15:59,746
[ GRUNTING ]

262
00:15:59,780 --> 00:16:01,546
DAMN IT!

263
00:16:01,580 --> 00:16:03,146
HOW AM I GONNA STOP IT?

264
00:16:03,180 --> 00:16:05,080
[ GROANING ]
DAMN DEMON.

265
00:16:05,113 --> 00:16:08,213
I'M GOING TO SNAP
THAT NECK OF YOURS.

266
00:16:08,246 --> 00:16:09,913
[ SUGURO ]
HOLD UP, YOU MORON.

267
00:16:09,946 --> 00:16:13,013
GO ON. TAKE A GOOD LOOK
AT YOURSELF.

268
00:16:13,046 --> 00:16:15,746
YOU TELL ME--
WHO'S THE REAL DEMON HERE?

269
00:16:15,780 --> 00:16:20,013
SHUT UP!
I'M FIGHTING TO PROTECT YOU.
TO PROTECT EVERYONE!

270
00:16:20,046 --> 00:16:22,380
OH, PISS OFF!
NOBODY ASKED YOU TO.

271
00:16:22,413 --> 00:16:25,346
COME ON, WAKE UP, KONEKOMARU!

272
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:26,780
BON.

273
00:16:26,813 --> 00:16:30,146
DON'T BE DECEIVED BY HIM.
THAT BOY IS JEALOUS
OF YOUR POWER.

274
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:33,246
JEALOUS! HURRY NOW.
KILL HIM.

275
00:16:33,280 --> 00:16:35,080
KILL THE SON OF SATAN!

276
00:16:35,113 --> 00:16:36,846
[ WHIMPERING ]

277
00:16:36,880 --> 00:16:39,046
[ RIN ]
CUT THE CRAP.

278
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,846
I DON'T WANT THIS.

279
00:16:40,880 --> 00:16:43,380
I NEVER ASKED
TO BE THE SON OF SATAN!

280
00:16:44,446 --> 00:16:46,113
[ GASPS ]

281
00:16:46,146 --> 00:16:48,380
[ GROANS ]
KONEKOMARU,

282
00:16:48,413 --> 00:16:53,580
IF YOU WANNA BE AFRAID OF ME,
THERE'S NOTHING I CAN DO.

283
00:16:53,613 --> 00:16:58,013
THING IS, WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU
THINKING TRUSTING THIS DEMON?

284
00:16:58,046 --> 00:16:59,846
THAT'S WHAT YOU GOT
YOUR FRIENDS FOR.

285
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:02,180
SHIMA AND SUGURO.

286
00:17:02,213 --> 00:17:04,346
YOUR FRIENDS GOT YOUR BACK,
NOT THAT THING!

287
00:17:10,213 --> 00:17:13,180
[ MIWA, THINKING ]
WHAT AM I DOING?

288
00:17:13,213 --> 00:17:15,980
EVEN IF I KILL OKUMURA,

289
00:17:16,013 --> 00:17:19,546
IT'S NOT GOING TO BRING BACK
MY MOM AND DAD.

290
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:20,846
I'M--

291
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,513
I'M--

292
00:17:24,380 --> 00:17:26,680
- [ GROANS ]
- DAMN YOU!

293
00:17:26,713 --> 00:17:27,913
[ GASPS ]

294
00:17:27,946 --> 00:17:29,346
WHERE'S HE GOING?
KONEKO!

295
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:33,780
I WON'T LET YOU ESCAPE.
YOU BELONG TO ME!

296
00:17:33,813 --> 00:17:36,680
[ ROARING ]

297
00:17:38,046 --> 00:17:40,346
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
RIN, STOP IT!

298
00:17:40,380 --> 00:17:43,013
YOU KNOW WHAT I'M DOING.
I'M GONNA SAVE HIM.

299
00:17:43,046 --> 00:17:44,013
[ BOTH GASP ]

300
00:17:44,046 --> 00:17:45,646
COME ON, KONEKOMARU!

301
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:46,880
[ GASPS ]

302
00:17:46,913 --> 00:17:49,446
COME ON, JUMP!
TRUST ME!

303
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:52,646
[ GRUNTING ]

304
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:55,113
[ BOTH SHOUTING ]

305
00:18:01,146 --> 00:18:02,513
[ BOTH GASP ]

306
00:18:02,546 --> 00:18:04,113
KONEKO!

307
00:18:04,146 --> 00:18:06,246
KONEKOMARU,
ARE YOU OKAY?

308
00:18:06,280 --> 00:18:08,280
[ GROANS ]
BON, SHIMA.

309
00:18:08,313 --> 00:18:11,813
- [ BOTH SIGH ]
- [ CRYING ]

310
00:18:11,846 --> 00:18:13,080
[ YUKIO ]
ARE YOU OKAY?

311
00:18:13,113 --> 00:18:15,513
I'M GOOD.

312
00:18:15,546 --> 00:18:17,080
NO BIG DEAL.

313
00:18:18,346 --> 00:18:21,046
[ MIWA ]
OKUMURA.
HUH?

314
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:23,213
[ CRYING ]

315
00:18:25,646 --> 00:18:27,480
I'M SORRY I TRIED TO--

316
00:18:29,046 --> 00:18:31,746
I'M SO SORRY.
[ CRYING CONTINUES ]

317
00:18:36,113 --> 00:18:39,180
[ MEPHISTO ]
SO IN THE END,
RIN OKUMURA SAVED MIWA.

318
00:18:39,213 --> 00:18:41,280
ANYONE ELSE HURT?

319
00:18:41,313 --> 00:18:45,080
WELL, SUGURO AND SHIMA.
A FEW BRUISES, THAT'S ALL.

320
00:18:45,113 --> 00:18:47,180
WELL, THAT'S GOOD TO HEAR.

321
00:18:47,213 --> 00:18:50,846
ALTHOUGH I'M STILL CONCERNED
ABOUT HOW THE DEMON
GOT THROUGH THE BARRIER.

322
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:55,180
WELL, THE ONLY WAY IT COULD
IS IF SOMEONE USED A KEY
TO OPEN A DOORWAY.

323
00:18:55,213 --> 00:18:57,013
PRETTY OBVIOUS, REALLY.

324
00:18:57,046 --> 00:18:59,280
THEN THE SITUATION
IS WORSE THAN I THOUGHT.

325
00:18:59,313 --> 00:19:03,580
ONLY A SELECT FEW ARE ALLOWED
THE USE OF MY KEYS, SO NOW
I'M REALLY CONCERNED.

326
00:19:03,613 --> 00:19:07,246
ME AND TSUBAKI FOUND THE DOORWAY
IN A PARKING LOT IN TOWN.

327
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:10,913
I WENT THROUGH IT AND FOUND
A TORCHED RESEARCH LAB
IN THIS BIG FOREST.

328
00:19:10,946 --> 00:19:13,380
- THAT'S SUSPICIOUS.
- UH-HUH.

329
00:19:13,413 --> 00:19:16,313
AND IT WASN'T YOUR TYPICAL
RESEARCH LAB EITHER.

330
00:19:16,346 --> 00:19:19,613
THEY WERE EXPERIMENTING
WITH ARTIFICIAL LIFE OUT THERE,

331
00:19:19,646 --> 00:19:22,980
SOMETHING THE VATICAN OUTLAWED
FOR THE LAST THREE CENTURIES.

332
00:19:23,013 --> 00:19:24,346
[ MEPHISTO ]
REALLY?

333
00:19:24,380 --> 00:19:26,813
NOW THAT <i>IS</i> INTRIGUING.

334
00:19:26,846 --> 00:19:30,346
WE SHOULD OPEN AN INVESTIGATION
INTO IT IMMEDIATELY.

335
00:19:32,346 --> 00:19:35,346
KONEKO, YOU'VE GOT
SOME VISITORS.

336
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:38,513
LOOK, I EVEN BROUGHT
SOME FINE LADIES ALONG
TO CHEER YOU--

337
00:19:38,546 --> 00:19:41,780
HUH?
[ KAMIKI ]
AND HE'S NOT HERE.

338
00:19:41,813 --> 00:19:43,613
I WONDER WHERE
HE'S GONE OFF TO.

339
00:19:45,146 --> 00:19:47,546
[ GASPS ]
DON'T TELL ME
HE'S THINKING ABOUT--

340
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:49,380
[ GRUNTS ]

341
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:52,546
[ VEHICLE APPROACHING ]

342
00:19:59,546 --> 00:20:00,713
[ GRUNTS ]

343
00:20:00,746 --> 00:20:02,880
COME ON, STOP MESSING ARO--

344
00:20:02,913 --> 00:20:05,513
WHAT UP?
O-OKUMURA.

345
00:20:05,546 --> 00:20:08,546
WHERE ARE YOU GOING
WITH THAT GINORMOUS BAG?
YOU DOING LAUNDRY?

346
00:20:08,580 --> 00:20:10,146
UH, UH--

347
00:20:10,180 --> 00:20:12,580
WHAT DO YOU CARE
WHERE I'M GOING?

348
00:20:12,613 --> 00:20:14,446
IT'S NOT LIKE IT'S
ANY OF YOUR BUSINESS.

349
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:15,513
HUH?

350
00:20:15,546 --> 00:20:18,613
AFTER MY PARENTS DIED,
I WAS ALL ALONE IN THE WORLD.

351
00:20:18,646 --> 00:20:21,980
THE HEAD MONK AT THE TEMPLE
TOOK ME IN AND RAISED ME
LIKE HIS OWN.

352
00:20:22,013 --> 00:20:26,446
I ALWAYS APPRECIATED
HIS KINDNESS, SO I MADE UP
MY MIND I'D PAY HIM BACK.

353
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:28,513
THAT'S WHY I CAME
TO THE ACADEMY WITH BON.

354
00:20:28,546 --> 00:20:31,646
TRUTH IS, I'M JUST
A SCAREDY CAT.

355
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:35,813
I'M TOTALLY USELESS,
SO I DECIDED TO QUIT.

356
00:20:35,846 --> 00:20:40,780
I'M ONLY GONNA GET
IN EVERYONE'S WAY IF I STAY HERE
ONE MINUTE LONGER.

357
00:20:40,813 --> 00:20:44,713
BACK UP.
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

358
00:20:44,746 --> 00:20:46,346
THAT I'LL BE IN EVERYONE'S WAY.

359
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:48,913
NO. BEFORE THAT.
I'M USELESS?

360
00:20:48,946 --> 00:20:51,213
BEFORE THAT!
HUH?
I DON'T KNOW.

361
00:20:51,246 --> 00:20:53,680
YOU SAID IT'S NONE
OF MY BUSINESS, DIDN'T YOU?

362
00:20:53,713 --> 00:20:56,146
HUH? THAT-THAT FAR?

363
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:58,380
DON'T SAY IT'S NOT
MY BUSINESS.

364
00:20:58,413 --> 00:21:03,546
IT IS, 'CAUSE BELIEVE IT OR NOT,
I THINK OF YOU AS MY FRIEND.

365
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:08,213
OKUMURA.
AND I'D BE SAD
IF MY FRIEND LEFT, YOU KNOW?

366
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:12,246
YOU'RE LYING.
NO, I'M NOT.

367
00:21:12,280 --> 00:21:14,613
STOP TRYING
TO MAKE ME FEEL BETTER.

368
00:21:14,646 --> 00:21:19,080
SUGARCOATING IT
IS NOT GONNA CHANGE THE FACT
THAT I TRIED TO KILL YOU.

369
00:21:19,113 --> 00:21:21,113
AND IF I GET POSSESSED
BY ANOTHER DEMON,

370
00:21:21,146 --> 00:21:23,246
WHO'S TO SAY I WON'T TRY AGAIN?

371
00:21:23,280 --> 00:21:27,246
THAT'S NOT WHAT FRIENDS DO,
SO HOW CAN YOU THINK OF ME
AS YOUR FRIEND?

372
00:21:27,280 --> 00:21:31,480
I KNOW, BUT YOU HAD FAITH
IN ME BACK THERE, REMEMBER?

373
00:21:31,513 --> 00:21:34,780
YOU DID.
AND I HAVE FAITH IN YOU TOO.

374
00:21:36,213 --> 00:21:39,446
THAT'S WHAT BEING FRIENDS
IS ALL ABOUT, ISN'T IT?

375
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:41,580
[ GASPS ]

376
00:21:41,613 --> 00:21:45,546
I MEAN, IF YOU WANT SOMEONE
TO TRUST YOU, Y-Y-YOU KNOW,
YOU--

377
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,713
YOU GOTTA HAVE
SOMETHING MORE THAN THAT.

378
00:21:47,746 --> 00:21:50,013
BUT THAT GUY, HE'S GOT
NOTHING ELSE TO OFFER.

379
00:21:50,046 --> 00:21:53,313
WOW, IT'S JUST LIKE BON SAID.

380
00:21:53,346 --> 00:21:56,280
YOU REALLY DON'T HAVE
ANYTHING ELSE TO OFFER,
DO YOU?

381
00:21:56,313 --> 00:21:59,713
HUH? HEY, MAN,
THAT'S KINDA RUDE.
I GOT LOTS TO OFFER.

382
00:21:59,746 --> 00:22:01,613
LIKE MONEY.
NO.

383
00:22:01,646 --> 00:22:03,046
TALENT?
YEAH, NO.

384
00:22:03,080 --> 00:22:06,346
[ SUGURO ] KONEKOMARU,
WHERE IN THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE GOING?

385
00:22:06,380 --> 00:22:08,380
WE'VE BEEN LOOKING
ALL OVER FOR YOU.

386
00:22:08,413 --> 00:22:10,080
BON! HI, GUYS!

387
00:22:10,113 --> 00:22:13,513
HEY! DON'T GO
SWOOPING IN LIKE THAT.
WE'RE HAVING A MOMENT HERE.

388
00:22:13,546 --> 00:22:15,313
[ SHIEMI ]
WHY IS HE SO ANGRY?

389
00:22:15,346 --> 00:22:17,513
[ SUGURO ]
IGNORE HIM.
STUPIDITY'S CONTAGIOUS.

390
00:22:17,546 --> 00:22:18,713
DON'T CALL ME STUPID.

391
00:22:18,746 --> 00:22:21,446
[ SHIMA ]
YOU STILL GOT SOME HEALING
TO DO, KONEKO.

392
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:23,846
OKUMURA CAN TAKE YOUR BAGS UP
FOR YOU.

393
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:25,746
[ RIN ]
WHY DO I HAVE TO?

394
00:22:25,780 --> 00:22:28,946
[ KAMIKI ]
IT'S THE LEAST YOU CAN DO.
YOU <i>ARE</i> HIS FRIEND, AREN'T YOU?

395
00:22:28,980 --> 00:22:30,646
GUESS I'M STUCK
WITH 'EM THEN.

396
00:22:40,013 --> 00:22:42,646
♪ [ WOMAN SINGING
IN JAPANESE ]

397
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:05,113
[ RIN ]
DO ME.
TELL MY FORTUNE NEXT.

398
00:24:05,146 --> 00:24:07,046
[ SHIMA ]
NOPE. DOESN'T WORK
FOR GUYS.

399
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:08,713
<i>HOW COME?</i>
<i>I'M A SPECIALIST.</i>

400
00:24:08,746 --> 00:24:11,080
GIRL FORTUNES ONLY.

401
00:24:11,113 --> 00:24:13,480
[ KAMIKI GIGGLING ]
THANK YOU, SHIMA.

402
00:24:13,513 --> 00:24:15,246
YOU'RE SWEET.

